{"type":"text","timestamp":1775877258866,"sessionID":"ses_28578fb30ffeorf2viCqvUA7BV","part":{"id":"prt_d7a882539001CcFTTVQDWoTU24","messageID":"msg_d7a881bcf00105PSNx0kKxNPkt","sessionID":"ses_28578fb30ffeorf2viCqvUA7BV","type":"text","text":"Now I have enough information to create a comprehensive verification report. Let me compile the findings:\n\n## Verification Report: AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient\n\n### Summary\n\n**Status:** ❌ **PARTIALLY IMPLEMENTED** - Missing required components\n\n### Spec Compliance Check\n\n#### ✅ Implemented Requirements\n\n| Requirement | Status | Evidence |\n|-------------|--------|----------|\n| `AgentRuntimeClient` class | ✅ | `agent_runtime.py:11-167` |\n| `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` class | ✅ | `clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py:13-148` |\n| Context manager protocol (`__enter__`, `__exit__`) | ✅ | `agent_runtime.py:105-120` |\n| Router URL resolution (arg → `ROUTER_URL` env → error) | ✅ | `agent_runtime.py:86-92` |\n| Session bootstrap via GET request | ✅ | `agent_runtime_data_plane.py:67-97` |\n| Payload invocation via POST | ✅ | `agent_runtime_data_plane.py:99-140` |\n| Timeout defaults (120s read / 5.0s connect) | ✅ | `agent_runtime.py:58`, `agent_runtime_data_plane.py:38-39` |\n| Per-call timeout override | ✅ | `agent_runtime.py:146-158`, `agent_runtime_data_plane.py:119-139` |\n| Session header `x-agentcube-session-id` | ✅ | `agent_runtime_data_plane.py:31` |\n| HTTP session with pooling (10/10) | ✅ | `agent_runtime_data_plane.py:63-65` |\n| Unit tests passing | ✅ | 32 passed, 3 skipped |\n\n#### ❌ Missing Required Components (Per Spec)\n\n| Component | Expected Path | Status |\n|-----------|--------------|--------|\n| `CodeInterpreterClient` | `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | ❌ MISSING |\n| Exception classes | `agentcube/exceptions.py` | ❌ MISSING |\n| `ControlPlaneClient` | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | ❌ MISSING |\n| `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | ❌ MISSING |\n| `read_token_from_file` utility | `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | ❌ MISSING |\n\n#### ❌ Export Compliance Issues\n\n**`agentcube/__init__.py`** (spec requirement):\n```python\n# SPEC REQUIRES:\nfrom .code_interpreter import CodeInterpreterClient\nfrom .agent_runtime import AgentRuntimeClient\n\n__all__ = [\"CodeInterpreterClient\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\"]\n```\n\n**Current implementation** only exports `AgentRuntimeClient`:\n```python\n# ACTUAL:\nfrom .agent_runtime import AgentRuntimeClient\n\n__all__ = [\"AgentRuntimeClient\"]\n```\n\n**`agentcube/clients/__init__.py`** (spec requirement):\n```python\n# SPEC REQUIRES:\n__all__ = [\n    \"ControlPlaneClient\",\n    \"CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\",\n    \"AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\",\n]\n```\n\n**Current implementation** only exports `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`:\n```python\n# ACTUAL:\n__all__ = [\"AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\"]\n```\n\n### Test Results\n\n```\n======================== 32 passed, 3 skipped in 0.08s =========================\n```\n\n- ✅ All unit tests pass (32 tests)\n- ⏭️ Integration tests skipped (require live Router)\n\n### Missing Files vs Spec\n\nPer the spec's **Package layout** table:\n\n| Path | Role | Status |\n|------|------|--------|\n| `pyproject.toml` | Package `agentcube-sdk`, dependencies | ✅ Exists |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | Public exports | ⚠️ Partial (missing CodeInterpreterClient export) |\n| `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | `CodeInterpreterClient` | ❌ MISSING |\n| `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | `AgentRuntimeClient` | ✅ Exists |\n| `agentcube/exceptions.py` | Exception classes | ❌ MISSING |\n| `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | Re-exports client classes | ⚠️ Partial |\n| `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` | ❌ MISSING |\n| `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` | ❌ MISSING |\n| `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` | ✅ Exists |\n| `agentcube/utils/http.py` | `create_session` | ✅ Exists |\n| `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | `read_token_from_file` | ❌ MISSING |\n| `agentcube/utils/log.py` | `get_logger` | ✅ Exists |\n| `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` | Empty (module marker) | ✅ Exists |\n\n### Conclusion\n\nThe **AgentRuntimeClient** implementation (core AR-028 feature) is **complete and tested**. However, the broader SDK structure defined in `/tmp/agentcube-ref/sdk-python/design.md` is **incomplete**:\n\n1. **CodeInterpreterClient** and related infrastructure are not implemented\n2. **Exception classes** module is missing  \n3. **ControlPlaneClient** and **CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient** are missing\n4. **Public exports** don't match spec (missing `CodeInterpreterClient`)\n\n**Recommendation:** If the scope is limited to AR-028 (AgentRuntimeClient only), the implementation is complete. If the full SDK design.md spec must be met, the missing components need to be implemented.","time":{"start":1775877258863,"end":1775877258863}}}
